The paper focuses on studying the interactions and links between users on multiple online social networks, specifically Twitter and Foursquare. This falls under the category of social networks and information retrieval, making cs.SI and cs.SOC the most likely categories. The paper also uses multilayer network analysis and link prediction, which could fall under cs.DS and cs.CYBER. Finally, the paper deals with location-based social networks, which could also place it under cs.IR.
